data.title: EFFAS Certified European Financial Analyst (CEFA) Holder List
data.meta_description: Get to know all EFFAS Certified European Financial Analyst worldwide. The most relevant financial certification.
data.text:
List as of May 3th, 2024, featuring EFFAS Certified European Financial Analyst (CEFA) holders who have granted consent for their names and country to be published on the website. EFFAS proudly certifies that the professionals listed here are accomplished EFFAS Certified European Financial Analyst (CEFA) holders.

If you are one of the more than 16,878 EFFAS Certified European Financial Analysts and wish to be included in this list, please contact your national society or write to certifications@effas.com. You will need to complete a consent form to register your willingness for your details to be published on the list.
